Natalie Lisinska https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Lisinska 0 Natalie Lisinska (born 11 January 1982) is a British-Canadian actress. Lisinska was born in Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England and grew up on Vancouver Island in British Columbia, attending St. Michaels University School. She studied drama at Ryerson University Theatre School. Natalie_Lisinska ( born 11_January_1982 ) is a_British-Canadian_actress .
